154
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:45,170
I don't want to leave here.

155
00:13:50,170 --> 00:13:53,740
Here's the key. Be sure
to lock up after you.

156
00:13:54,610 --> 00:13:56,550
Manager!

157
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:05,360
Kikugorô, you've
stepped up the ladder.

158
00:14:07,090 --> 00:14:11,800
But... I never thought
about leaving here.

159
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:17,540
What is your dream?
To work here?

160
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:19,870
